      <title>News24 称南非商业中心可能面临供水限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/south-africa-s-commercial-hub-may-face-water-curbs-news24-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 News24 援引南非水务与卫生部门的报告称，南非的商业中心豪登省明年可能面临供水限制，因为大宗供水企业的用水量已超过允许量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/south-africa-s-commercial-hub-may-face-water-curbs-news24-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 09:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
