      <title>美联储降息数小时后巴西将加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/brazil-readies-interest-rate-hike-diverging-with-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济过热和通胀预期高于目标，巴西央行成为美联储推动的全球宽松政策中的异类，巴西央行很可能自 2022 年以来首次加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/brazil-readies-interest-rate-hike-diverging-with-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
